{"tid":338313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天怒人怨] 再有市民一地兩檢提覆核 禁制提請人大","createTime":"2017-07-28T05:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T00:42:55.000Z","uid":77196,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc40ba7b43db7bc8b0e55120284e8582f44a3a4","tid":338313,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T05:46:45.000Z","msg":"再有市民就高鐵實施「一地兩檢」入稟高等法院提請司法覆核，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>質疑有關決定未有向公眾諮詢，違反《基本法》</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n申請人張德榮表示，「一地兩檢」出賣港人於司法管理權的利益，他不同意以租賃方式劃出內地口岸區，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>亦不滿意政府用香港公帑建造高鐵，但供內地使用，要求法庭禁制特區政府在沒有港人共識前，將相關決定提請人大</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n以人數計，張德榮是第5位就「一地兩檢」提請司法覆核的人士；答辯人分別為特首林鄭月娥及行政會議成員。"},{"pid":"6efa2a49310bb538834dde140aa1d6cb880b847b","tid":338313,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T05:48:26.000Z","msg":"香港唔提淫大都可以自己釋法<br />\n佢自己就係法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ec8010d1e6c6eac43ea82b76007e4332994cce","tid":338313,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"釋法ko晒"},{"pid":"0e482b12d5128d1bae522b13bde90115209bb6e4","tid":338313,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eda77bc7c2cda7a5cfed89800f854b737e7a979","tid":338313,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"五毛唔敢入依個post"},{"pid":"b20ca2933a87760deac9bbc709b554f08d1e6301","tid":338313,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超多JR, 而且唔同層面"},{"pid":"112fcf3f65e5dc87d50bc22a55deeca11b8f9b8e","tid":338313,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:06:49.000Z","msg":"琴日有80個人去示威！<br />\n<br />\n你地睇到民意未？"},{"pid":"74085ed0dd5883a7fd77980f5221a5bfa343fabb","tid":338313,"uid":102110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再有市民就高鐵實施「一地兩檢」入稟高等法院提請司法覆核，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>質疑有關決定未有向公眾諮詢，違反《基本法》</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n申請人張德榮表示，「一地兩檢」出賣港人於司法管理權的利益，他不同意以租賃方式劃出內地口岸區，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>亦不滿意政府用香港公帑建造高鐵，但供內地使用，要求法庭禁制特區政府在沒有港人共識前，將相關決定提請人大</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n以人數計，張德榮是第5位就「一地兩檢」提請司法覆核的人士；答辯人分別為特首林鄭月娥及行政會議成員。</blockquote><br />\n提請人大？香港內部問題自己解決得了。法庭判一地兩檢違反基本法得了。人大釋法，不了"},{"pid":"50c68ee26511da546d61e9317b596d358ea30d82","tid":338313,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b04cae83c73461a0ee296766606194c2bcd363e","tid":338313,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"呢d真係關乎公眾利益"},{"pid":"c9d472355094f37f0948584994993973134fb70b","tid":338313,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"黎緊幾個月會不斷有報導會屌呢班人阻住通車<br />\nIn fact 早兩日已有報紙做頭版暗屌緊"},{"pid":"83247ee83996adadb59da725663d8b8d906db655","tid":338313,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:02:20.000Z","msg":"咁就睇得出仲有幾多份報紙仲係講人話"},{"pid":"949762796ede9e95f839b4affe2028acade597c2","tid":338313,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"呢個post理應置頂，而大家可以幫手update下邊份報紙邊一日屌過人地阻高鐵通車<br />\n從而整合賣港媒體list"},{"pid":"a259a42dbb974238ac24f632bd7e95c5aad42a31","tid":338313,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"有d似之前阻領匯上市一幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b86993ec9e13cd81b5a2400d5965a9b00cf138","tid":338313,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a37e46d77ad2ea9ed669e5cd4c210359722